Practical 1 – Product of 4 Numbers
Login.aspx
<form id="form1" runat="server">

Enter Number 1:
<asp:TextBox ID="txt1" runat="server"></asp:TextBox><br/>

Enter Number 2:
<asp:TextBox ID="txt2" runat="server"></asp:TextBox><br/>

Enter Number 3:
